{"word":"ἐπαισχύνομαι","slug":"ἐπαισχύνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαισχύνομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-αισχυνθήσομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to be ashamed at</i> or <i>of</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>τινα</el> or <el>τι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to be ashamed</i> to do, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <i>to be ashamed of</i> doing or having done a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/>"}]}